<Author>Tiffany627
<Content>We liked it!! My friend and I stayed at the Hotel Villa del Sol and we thought it was great. We stayed in room 205 and it was very clean, did not stink, and had no bugs. The air conditioner worked and our water pressure although not very strong, did the job (The water pressure throughout the entire island is not strong so I do not blame the hotel). We thought the hotel was very cute but wished that the pool did not close as early as it does which is 6 pm. The lady at the bar is VERY nice and made me a great pina colada and a delicious burger for my friend. Overall, I have no complaints and plan on going back to the island next year and staying at the Hotel Villa del Sol with my husband. 
